4.17/5  rDev -5.4%look: 4 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 3Review #100 on BA. Figured I'd get there before I hit 1000 over on RB. This review is transcribed from an RB review, consumed in 2007. Paid $12 for a 1 ounce pour at House of Brews on 46th St. in NYC. This is very overpriced, but less so if you think of it as a nice sipping liqueur.
